data.description: Nice Solid 3 Bedroom 2 bath House with a massive stone fireplace to enjoy those cozy evenings at home. Appliances are fabulous and the is a nice screened porch on the back.  Extra storage shed for your things. Close to town and and minutes to shopping and restaurants in the Villages or Eustis. Come home to peace and quite, this home will not last long.....  All measurements are approximate and the Buyers responsibility to confirm. The house does need some updates/upgrades that may restrict buyers from getting FHA, VA, or similar financing.  Roof installed in 2005.
